{"tid":2025872,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一個制衡屎家軍嘅簡單方法","createTime":"2020-05-20T14:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T02:01:11.000Z","uid":291448,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"14c833560d55ae9b54d4e9946d35291fa7ca0f58","tid":2025872,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:23:40.000Z","msg":"就係大力支持黃圈手足頻道高手紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早喺反送中果陣 高手紹已經開始不斷剪輯香港黑警D柒嘢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ubHTRvvQe6U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FubHTRvvQe6U&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=ead36dc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ubHTRvvQe6U</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DGHxbvEOWaU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDGHxbvEOWaU&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=9155b84e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DGHxbvEOWaU</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZET0eZ3C6HA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZET0eZ3C6HA&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=871e4acd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZET0eZ3C6HA</a> <br />\n跟住亦都有剪輯啲藍絲嘅柒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pfRfLn2QMrE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpfRfLn2QMrE&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=15d0a4e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pfRfLn2QMrE</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/09fPl6leszs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F09fPl6leszs&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=a1a44bc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/09fPl6leszs</a> <br />\n同時亦都有剪輯反送中嘅感動時刻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hJK7wBVkk_A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhJK7wBVkk_A&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=06988299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hJK7wBVkk_A</a> <br />\n仲有剪輯啲為香港做實事嘅議員政治人物合集<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ME8WLcQ6tEw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FME8WLcQ6tEw&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=8045093d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ME8WLcQ6tEw</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JGWmy9GEBrg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJGWmy9GEBrg&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=aece86fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JGWmy9GEBrg</a> <br />\n佢個頻道其實仲有好多好正嘅影片<br />\n大家可以入去佢個頻道度探索下 <br />\n高手紹 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCiLcOaifs-1KxslIYs20JZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCiLcOaifs-1KxslIYs20JZg&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=1d165652\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCiLcOaifs-1KxslIYs20JZg</a><br />\n記住大力支持CLS佢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果啲咩屎家軍其實退訂退Like佢地 <br />\n轉而大力支持自己黃圈手足頻道 佢地自然就會收皮<br />\n不過當然除左高手紹呢個黃圈手足頻道之外<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有好多黃圈手足頻道都要大力支持㗎 詳情請留意以下TG頻道</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/OccupyYoutube\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FOccupyYoutube&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=f66557dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/OccupyYoutube</a>"},{"pid":"97f50e872f9054d6dbb05ff6ada961cd6c7c2d9a","tid":2025872,"uid":224277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime